{"tid":723151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"削髮明志！美斯換新Look望破咒","createTime":"2018-06-30T07:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T16:01:13.000Z","uid":33799,"like":90,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"7291d13f57c5feddded99f5f8c16015a16b915dc","tid":723151,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sNLOmuSx.u7tnra95S9KFg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/on_cc__539/77d42e41119cee2e2bf90d0870e1e4be\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsNLOmuSx.u7tnra95S9KFg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fon_cc__539%2F77d42e41119cee2e2bf90d0870e1e4be&h=a721fbac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿根廷今晚10點與法國爭逐16強，對美斯來講若想晉級，就要破解生涯的一個大魔咒，他過去三次參加世界盃，從未在淘汰賽中入球。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">既然想破咒，就先來「削髮明志」，這位阿根廷球王就拉隊，與隊友齊齊剪頭髮，希望可以改一改運氣，美斯的新髮型兩邊剷青，睇落都爽晒。</span><br />\n<br />\n睇番美斯過去三屆世盃，06年小組賽對住塞黑入了處子球，但在淘汰賽則沒有入球球，最後被德國淘汰；10年在馬納當拿領軍下，在淘汰賽又被德國踢走，2016年他第三次去世界盃，個人首次躋身決賽，但被德國在加時絕殺，而他在小組賽攻入了四球，但在淘汰賽亦是「食白果」。<br />\n<br />\n已經All in 阿根廷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682977ac10456a54f59f40f53474623367e2c9d8","tid":723151,"uid":33799,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">在7月1日與法國爭奪世界盃8強門票賽前，阿根廷總教練Jorge Sampaoli呼籲他的子弟兵要將自己的表現提升到「天才」Lionel Messi的水準。</span><br />\n<br />\n首戰震撼性以地1比1與冰島踢平的比賽中，Messi錯失12碼罰球，為阿根廷本屆到目前為止不完善的爭冠努力定調。<br />\n<br />\n這位31歲的巴塞隆納好手，隨後在備受譴責的0比3敗給克羅埃西亞，阿根廷防守弱點暴露無遺，進攻乏力的比賽中幾乎等於隱形。<br />\n<br />\n靠著隊友Ever Banega出色的傳球，Messi才終於在2比1擊敗奈及利亞的比賽中於俄羅斯首開紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n儘管Messi在本屆賽事遇到麻煩，備受批評的Sampaoli還是呼籲他的隊友們要給這位「地球上最佳球員」盡可能最多的幫助。<br />\n<br />\n「在足球上Leo有如此清晰的視野，讓我們看到有時候只有天才才能看到的事情。」Sampaoli說。<br />\n<br />\n「通常要達到如此優秀球員的水準是很困難的事情，他對我們所有人來說都是耀眼的光芒，我們必須盡全力試著跟上他的水準。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d1bfc9a75373751c332fb6f409adbf04aeb33b","tid":723151,"uid":21469,"like":165,"dislike":5,"score":160,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:06:18.000Z","msg":"剷左啲鬚好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235c3855212bb87af5285ef89d2c69a422bfb6cd","tid":723151,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27d1bfc9a75373751c332fb6f409adbf04aeb33b","tid":723151,"uid":21469,"like":165,"dislike":5,"score":160,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:06:18.000Z","msg":"剷左啲鬚好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"咪係"},{"pid":"a39543cbcdec3d903da94a466077c86b38f175f0","tid":723151,"uid":34771,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"個fade幾靚"},{"pid":"ff8195298a5f9a3b482145972d89de47ec88dbc0","tid":723151,"uid":128014,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"著名反油頭打手大寶gor仲未入嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f30bd47de0e4167877eec8480e2ea886b3c4781","tid":723151,"uid":28758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"有美沙就夠"},{"pid":"a95aa3fa513e59d9e951ada3748e052715d4ee8e","tid":723151,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:17:18.000Z","msg":"唔係今晚咩？"},{"pid":"68ca748ed7880ad6d07fa3647eda377bb4a237a8","tid":723151,"uid":34490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"ci